description: Many times I find myself wondering what is the chaos that I disguise as peace, what is it really important for me to see in order to be able to properly observe my own chaos and remove that disguise of peace, to be really aware of the chaos that makes me live, that makes me able to continue generating chaos that I cannot disguise as peace, to be able to continue living a chaotic life in an authentic chaotic world and not wanting to evoke peace that will end up killing me slowly and agonizingly...
